 some money. You had to be a - a source of family income. That - exactly is what it used to be, now - if you could earn a bob or two - or a copper or two, don't say a bob or two, you could earn a copper or two then you was an assent to the family, a great
 assent to the family, so that's how - they used to look upon children. I won't say every family was like that, I won't say, but my family was definitely desp}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11089250\charrsid11078316 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
