rdcage, oh about - nine inches - long, about six inches deep and about four inches wide. Wired - half way up wired, in a black handkerchief, and he used to sing, and they - and the bird could sing better when it was - in the dark. So they used to - take t
h
e bird - in a black handkerchief, and they used to sit and - used to be - contests who bird was singing the best in these pubs, that was every Sunday that was that - that used to happen every Sunday. As far as I - Saturday I suppose as well but I know it 
