sed to happen at the weekends. And you'd see them all - whippet racing, over the Marshes. Tottenham Marshes and - and - and - and Hackney Marshes used to be - full of - cock fighting and all, I've seen cock fighting. Bantam fighting, yes, bantam. Bantam f
i
ghts. Used to have the old bantam cock. Used to have rare old bantam fight. Mind you it became - a bit of a racket, they had to stop it in the finish. 'Cos it was - blood sport really I suppose, a blood sport. Used to have bamtam fights. Cock fights. Oh y
es. And - used to be football teams and all you see, every - there was more football teams about. As well, more football teams.
