y used to have their own - they caught the train, you know I told you there was a difference in the trains. The office workers used to get the twenty past seven train, or after twenty past seven when there was no - cheap fare, they used to pay - pay the f
u
ll fare. Twenty past seven. They was - they were quite - yes, they used to always be the - rolled umbrella and the bowler hat business, and the frock coat. Pin stripe, if you - if you - if you wanted to be somebody and look somebody you had a pin striped 
trousers and a black coat and west}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8024667\charrsid11078316  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15817354\charrsid11078316 coat and pin striped trousers.
