oever - who - was ever you spoken to. But you - you never spoke to - the affluent people without some intrepidation, you - you realized - you realized you was up - up against a barrier.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7218946 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15817354\charrsid11078316 Was there anyone you called sir or master?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10358713 SB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15817354\charrsid11078316 Oh everybody you
 called sir, you had to say sir to. Anybody that was any good at all, you had to say sir to 'em because if you didn't - he'd say, who are you talking to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7218946 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15817354\charrsid11078316 Do you remember anyone showing respect to your parents in this way?
