 people. I'm telling you - with - without - the - the real - the real - people with money - would respect any - poorer person with - sort of - respect, they would not - they would not - just because you happened to be poor they would not give you the - br
ush off. They would really be gentleman. You could always tell a gentleman in those days and a lady. You could always - it was only the - in betweens who got a bit snooty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7218946 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15817354\charrsid11078316 What would you describe as a real gentleman or a real lady then?
