d
 have - a milkman - a milkman would deliver. And of course they used to have it 'cos everybody went out early to work. See, and there was - there was a distinction - too, I mean to say, there was the - there was the - pin striped trousers - black coat and
 waistcoat and pin striped trousers were fellow who was mostly white collared, and he had a briefcase then and the saying was, oh he's gone to work with his bread and drip}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8024667\charrsid11078316 p}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
