\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10358713 SB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15817354\charrsid11078316 Yes, one - used to say, hello he's gone to work with his bread and dripping in his briefcase, you know, that was how the attitude was.

