sed to say, well you - you - you have this, Stanley. You had this - what I earnt used to bring home, show to mum. You was very pleased to show it to mum what you'd got, you - you pulled your pockets out and mum - you knew mum was delighted and mum - mothe
r
 would reward you, put it that way. In a fair way of doing it you see. She knew you'd earnt money, she - she was glad of it. She was glad of the extra copper. You piled the whole lot out, you never argued with your mother. There were some people who used 
to say I let my mum know, but - their mother - would find 'em out, used to - used to get a copper in. The mother find 'em out - the mother used to know in those days what they was doing of. You was out carol singing.
