r
ict messenger? That's a lovely job they said. So I said, right, I'll be a district messenger. So - you was given a uniform - with nice - silver buttons. Pair of trousers with a - white - silver stripe round the side and - you was given clothes to wear. Th
ey never give you the things that you wanted, that was a pair of boots, they never give you them. But - they give you the pair of trousers and the un}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16476657\charrsid11078316 ifo}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
