e park, or take a child out for a walk - say you - you'd have to report to a - certain hotel and a Mrs So and so at a certain hotel and she'd tell you - she wants her dog taken out for a walk in Hyde Park for an hour or something like that or - she - if y
o
u - if you looked - capable they used to entrust your child with her you see - with you, you see, and you was - or - or lese you used to be asked to go to a - take your turn in a theatre queue, 'til they arrived you see, buy a ticket, they'd give you the 
