oney to buy a ticket. You'd stand in the queue, something like that and - then they arrive you simply gave way - they used to take you - you may be there an hour, something like that, it don't matter if it was in the rain or not, they - you - you was paid
 
to be in the rain so you had to stop in the blooming rain. So that's how - that's the sort of things, but when you come to a - I was sent to Shoreditch. On a Boxing Day. Sent to Shoreditch, I believe I told you did I, sent to Shoreditch on a Boxing Day. A
n
