boy job, took it home. No, no, I got - that was after I think - the pageboy job was - when I first went out to wirk but the very first job - from - from Randall's. 'Cos I never got paid weekly, I was - kept in and I - pageboy I was kept in and I had about
 two bob a week, and - that was a - that was me lot because I was - board and lodgings was included into it. But the actual first weekly wage for working - daily, was at Randall}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16476657\charrsid11078316 \rquote }{
